## 📌 Project Overview

This project is designed to simulate a real-world healthcare platform where:

- Patients can register, login, and analyze medical reports
- Doctors can access dashboards and patient insights
- AI analyzes medical text and provides structured output

---

## ✨ Features

### 🔐 Authentication
- Secure Signup & Login
- Password hashing using bcrypt
- JWT-based authentication
- Role-based access (Patient / Doctor)

---

### 👤 Patient Portal
- Login system
- Dashboard UI
- Submit medical reports
- AI-powered analysis
- View results:
  - Summary
  - Possible Condition
  - Risk Level
  - Recommendations

---

### 👨‍⚕️ Doctor Portal
- Separate login page
- Doctor dashboard UI
- View patient alerts (UI ready)
- AI suggestions (UI ready)

