## 🚀 Features

### 👤 Authentication System
- User Signup (Patient / Doctor)
- Secure Login using JWT
- Password hashing with bcrypt
- Role-based redirection

### 🧑‍⚕️ Patient Portal
- Login dashboard
- Submit medical reports
- AI-based analysis
- View results (summary, condition, risk, recommendations)

### 👨‍⚕️ Doctor Dashboard
- Doctor login
- Patient overview (UI ready)
- Alerts & AI suggestions

### 🤖 AI Integration
- Uses OpenRouter API (GPT-based model)
- Converts medical text into structured JSON:
  - Summary
  - Possible condition
  - Risk level
  - Recommendations

### 🌐 Deployment
- Backend deployed on **Render**
- Frontend deployed on **Vercel**
- Fully working live application

